These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 10

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, tea, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, hiking, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, rock, folk, jazz
 1. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan jazz##3
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the fan rock##6
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking tea or the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan folk, but not both##10
 6. the person drinking tea and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the fan jazz##5
 9. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | juice | tea   | mirinda      | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks     | hiking | writing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | country | jazz         | rock     |

