.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, corn, cucumber, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, dutch, malaysian, british
4 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, turtle, guinea-pig
 1. the colombian is the person eating tomato or the owner of the guinea-pig is the colombian, but not both##10
 2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 3. the colombian is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
 4. the owner of the turtle and the colombian have different parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
 8. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 9. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
11. the british is in an even position##4
12. the colombian is the person eating pear or the colombian is the owner of the guinea-pig, but not both##10
13. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | corn    | pear | cucumber    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | colombian | dutch  | british |
| Pet           | turtle     | guinea-pig    | goat    | ferret    |

