1. the person eating mango is the pakistani##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
3. the person eating mango is the british or the person eating mango is the person drinking iced-tea, but not both##10
4. the person eating lemon is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
5. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the german is between the person eating banana and the pakistani##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage      | water         | lemonade     | iced-tea | milk |
| Food          | banana | artichoke | mango         | lemon   |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | german   | pakistani       | british   |

