.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-4::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cranberry, cucumber, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, puzzles, traveling, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, malaysian, nigerian
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the mexican##6
 6. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the malaysian or the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating cranberry, but not both##10
 8. the malaysian is the person eating cucumber or the malaysian is the person who's hobby is puzzles, but not both##10
 9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person eating cucumber##7
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime  | eggplant   | cranberry | cucumber  |
| Hobby         | board-games     | traveling  | puzzles | video-games |
| Nationality   | mexican | argentine | nigerian  | malaysian |

