.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, fanta, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, documentary, time-travel, adventure
4 different pets are kept: snake, horse, chinchilla, frog
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the snake is not the person watching documentary movies##6
 3. the owner of the horse is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person watching adventure movies##6
 5. the owner of the frog and the person watching fantasy movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person drinking tea is the person watching fantasy movies or the person drinking tea is the owner of the snake, but not both##10
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking milk##7
12. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | tea   | milk | almond-milk | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | documentary    | fantasy   | adventure |
| Pet           | snake    | horse | chinchilla    | frog  |

