There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, canadian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, bus, skateboard
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 2. the colombian is the person who's hobby is woodworking or the colombian is the person driving the skateboard, but not both##10
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 4. the person driving the snowmobile and the polish have different parity positions##9
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the polish is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 7. the japanese is on the far right##1
 8. the canadian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the colombian##7
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the polish is between the person driving the bus and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | video-games | filmmaking  | skydiving |
| Nationality   | colombian  | canadian      | polish | japanese |
| Transport     | jet-ski | snowmobile       | skateboard    | bus   |

