The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, manager, chef, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat, fish, snake
 1. the person eating onion is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
 2. the accountant is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person eating onion##2
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the owner of the goat##7
 5. the owner of the goat and the person eating pumpkin have the same parity positions##9
 6. the manager is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the chef is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the accountant or the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating lemon, but not both##10
10. the owner of the guinea-pig and the manager have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |       3        |     4      |
| Food   | lemon    | pumpkin     | onion         | cucumber |
| Job    | manager | accountant    | chef | social-worker    |
| Pet    | guinea-pig      | goat | fish            | snake   |

