 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4
 5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
 6. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
