.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-10-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, grapefruit, corn, peas
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, musical, superhero
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, goat, bird
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 2. the owner of the fish is the person watching musical movies or the owner of the fish is the person eating lemon, but not both##10
 3. the person eating corn is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
 4. the person eating corn is not to the left of the owner of the fish##8
 5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
 6. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the goat##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
10. the owner of the snake is not the person watching superhero movies##6
11. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
12. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
13. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
14. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | grapefruit   | lemon | peas  | corn        |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | superhero      | musical    | satire |
| Pet           | goat   | bird    | fish | snake      |

 